data.description:
Newly renovated lower unit in old Brooklyn with updated features. Shared laundry/storage facilities available in the basement. Off-street garage parking provided. Enjoy the fully fenced backyard. Tenant responsible for gas/electric utilities. Immediate availability for occupancy.

Minimal one year lease. Owner assumes responsibility for water, sewer, and trash services. Tenants are responsible for electric and gas utilities. Indoor smoking is strictly prohibited, while vaping is permitted. Shared driveway with designated spot in two car garage. Small pets allowed with $500 security deposit.
